"China NICU hospital preterm baby prognosis quality improvement project" through 4 years of unremitting efforts, including tens of thousands of preterm infants with a gestational age of 33 weeks and below, so that the domestic small gestational age and small birth weight premature birth mortality decreased by 1/3, while the incidence of serious complications of preterm infants significantly decreased, greatly improving the quality of premature baby.
