The General Administration of Market Supervision recently issued the "Notice on Strengthening the Supervision of Market Prices during the Mid-Autumn Festival National Day in 2018", which requires strengthening price supervision in the field of housing rental and real estate, severely rectifying price collusion, hoarding rental sources, fabricating false information to inflate rents, charging fees in bundled services, publishing misleading price information, and unspecified price violations.
The notice is clear, it is necessary to strengthen price monitoring and early warning, and pay close attention to market price dynamics.
All localities should pay close attention to the necessities of life such as large-volume grain, oil, meat, poultry, egg and vegetable milk salt, as well as the market and price changes of local residents' holiday consumption of special commodities, and strengthen price monitoring and analysis of early warning.
Once the tendency and early problems of market fluctuations are found, timely measures are taken to effectively resolve them.
It is necessary to strengthen the supervision and inspection of the wholesale and retail links of daily necessities, increase the frequency and supervision of places closely related to the daily consumption of the masses, and urge operators to abide by the law and operate in good faith.
The notice pointed out that it is necessary to strengthen the inspection of key areas and create a good holiday consumption environment; strengthen the supervision of the ticket price of state-owned scenic spots; focus on investigating and punishing the state-owned scenic spots not to implement the price level or floating range stipulated by the government, increase the charging items without authorization, increase the ticket price in the form of illegal settings of "parks" tickets, high pricing discounts, bundled sales, not according to the provisions of the price, do not implement preferential measures, price increases, mandatory charging and other illegal activities.
The notice requires that the price supervision of daily necessities, especially agricultural products, be strengthened.
Affected by seasonal changes, natural disasters and sudden epidemics, the prices of vegetables, pork and other essential agricultural products in some areas have fluctuated recently.
All localities should combine local actual conditions to effectively strengthen the market price supervision of agricultural and sideline products, cooperate with relevant departments to do a good job in stabilizing production and market supply, and organize forces to carry out key market inspections and random spot checks.
For commodities such as pork with tight supply and faster price increases, increase the frequency of inspections, and seriously investigate and deal with illegal acts such as hoarding, raising prices, and collusively raising prices.
The notice pointed out that it is necessary to strengthen price supervision in the field of housing rental and real estate.
Mid-Autumn Festival, National Day coincides with the peak season of housing rental and commercial housing sales, all localities should pay close attention to the price behavior of real estate enterprises, intermediary companies and housing rental-related enterprises, strictly rectify the rent price collusion, hoarding rental sources, fabricate false information to raise rent, bundled service methods to charge fees, publish misleading price information, unknown code price and other price violations, increase the sale of hot real estate and real estate intermediaries to investigate the market.The real estate market environment creates an open and transparent real estate market price order.
The notice mentioned that all localities should do a good job in price supervision in other links of the tourism industry, focus on standardizing the price order of catering, accommodation, shopping, sightseeing, entertainment, parking and other links, guide operators to do a good job of marking prices and charging publicity, and seriously investigate and deal with various price violations.
The notice said that it is necessary to strengthen the inspection of transportation prices such as roads, railways, civil aviation, and water transport, and seriously investigate and deal with illegal acts such as illegal price increases, extra-price charges, and price-markings that are not marked in accordance with regulations.
Implement the "green channel" for the transportation of fresh agricultural products and the exemption of small bus tolls on major holidays.
It is necessary to innovate regulatory measures and working methods, strengthen the publicity of price laws and regulations of online and offline commodity retail enterprises and e-commerce platforms, urge operators to improve price promotion programs, and investigate and deal with fictitious original prices, misleading price labeling, and non-fulfilment of price commitments.
