Beijing News (Reporter Ni Wei) The State Administration of Radio, Television and Television issued the "Notice on Carrying out Special Remediation of Radio and Television Advertising" on September 29, and has carried out special rectification of radio and television advertising from now until the end of this year.
The rectification content includes advertisements with vulgar content, low style and low taste problems, and medical health programs that broadcast problems without record management.
According to the notice, the focus of this special rectification focus on nine aspects of search and rectification.
Specifically, there are: advertising that has guiding problems; advertisements with vulgar content, style and low taste problems; advertisements that exceed the time and do not play problems in accordance with regulations; there are medical, pharmaceutical, medical equipment, medical equipment, health food, cosmetics, beauty and other advertising such as exaggerated false propaganda, misleading the audience, misleading the audience, etc., such as medical, pharmaceutical, medical equipment, health food, cosmetics, beauty, etc., and medical health programs that have unrecorded management.There are problems that the broadcast time and frequency of public service advertisements do not meet the requirements of the regulations; there are problems of inadequate advertising broadcasting management system, lax censorship and inadequate implementation of responsibilities; there are advertisements with other illegal and illegal problems.
The remediation work will be fully covered in the country, the rectification and standardization requirements are fully implemented to all levels of radio and television media, channel frequencies, programs and periods, "no blind spots, no dead spots, no exceptions."
The notice requires that the radio and television administrative departments at all levels shall deal with all kinds of illegal and illegal advertisements found in the supervision and inspection in strict accordance with the Measures of the General Administration of Radio and Television Broadcasting Institutions for Illegal Handling.
If the violation is serious, it is necessary to give serious treatment such as admonition talk, notification of criticism, suspension of advertising broadcast until the broadcast of the frequency channel is suspended, and expose to the public according to the situation.
In recent years, the SARFT has repeatedly stopped illegal advertising.
This year, the State Administration of Radio and Television issued a notice to publicly stop the advertising of "0 soaked fruit milk", "sava cocktail", "Bonrit plant anti-breeding and hair loss" and other serious violations such as exaggerated propaganda and misleading audience.
The SARFT has formulated a number of regulations and notices to regulate the advertising behavior of radio and television broadcasts.
The "Notice on Further Strengthening the Advertising Management of TV Shopping Short Films on the Wei Video Road" stipulates that all video channels shall not broadcast TV shopping short films within the period from 18:00 to 24 o'clock every day.
Other times broadcast TV shopping shorts advertising, shall not use the host for publicity, shall not use the "sell" exaggerated dubbing, tone, action and other publicity, shall not use "orthomorphic", "plastic", "fat", "fat" and other publicity or disguised publicity breast-rich, weight-loss products, every hourly broadcast of TV shopping shorts advertising shall not exceed 1 (times), each shall not exceed 3 minutes.
The "Notice on Further Strengthening the Management of Radio and Television Advertising" stipulates that when television stations are inserted advertisements in the middle of film and television dramas, they must strictly abide by the provisions of Decree No. 61 of the General Administration: 2 commercial advertisements can be inserted in each episode of non-golden time (in 45 minutes), each time shall not exceed 1 minute and 30 seconds; the prime time (19:00 to 21:00) each concentration can be inserted 1 commercial advertisement, the duration of the advertisement shall not exceed 1 minute;
The notice also stipulates that radio and television broadcasting institutions should strictly review the qualifications, certificates and other legal materials for health information advertisements such as medical, pharmaceutical, medical devices, and health food, and resolutely prohibit the broadcast of sexual advertising.
To regulate the form of health information advertising, you must not publish advertisements in the form of health information special programs.
The health information special program should focus on introducing scientific knowledge such as disease prevention, control and treatment, and must not contain advertising content such as medical, pharmaceutical, medical equipment, health food, etc., and must not be proved in the name of patients and doctors, pharmacists, experts, etc.
