While the guests enjoyed the superb performance of Chinese artists, they praised the local love.
Wu Changmao, president of the China Association, said that China's rapid progress and development have made the Chinese children overseas feel proud.
2018 coincides with the 200th anniversary of the arrival of the Chinese people in Australia, and overseas Chinese will continue to carry forward the fine tradition of 200 years, integrate more actively into the mainstream society, be a strong bond of friendship between China and Australia, and make unremitting efforts for the economic development and social progress of the two countries.
On the same day, the Botswana China Association for the Promotion of Peaceful Reunification and the Chinese Charity Foundation, the Botswana Chinese Overseas Chinese Chamber of Commerce and the Gaborone China Aid Center jointly held the "2018 Overseas Chinese Community Association" in Gaborone.
