Lawyer carrying an axe to court session?
The news was really exciting at first glance, and it also exploded in the legal circle.
Fujian Quanzhou City Law then fined the lawyers involved 500 yuan, and recommended in writing that the Quanzhou City Bar Association investigate and deal with it.
According to the Beijing News, the Quanzhou Municipal Law Association issued a formal notice that the behavior of the two lawyers does not involve illegal activities and is not punished according to law.
From the perspective of multiple reports, the treatment of the Quanzhou Municipal Law Association is not short-term or confrontation, but has been recognized by Quanzhou Middle Court.
An event that could have caused tension within the legal community was eventually properly resolved.
The reversal of the matter stems from a more complete truth reduction: the axe carried by the lawyer involved is the same style and model as the defendant's murder weapon, but it is not open-ended, and only provides auxiliary evidence in the cross-examination of evidence, and there is no subjective intention of intimidating actions or "endangering the safety of the court".
To determine whether the lawyer's behavior is illegal or not, four very important details need to pay attention to: First, the local court has held two sessions before, only showing the axe photo, from the defense point of view, it is necessary to show the axe original; second, the axe is to buy it one hour before the court, not the lawyer is unwilling to seek the consent of the judge, but objectively failed to contact the judge; third, the entire axe has not been overtired or improperly used; fourth, the lawyer in question was publicly admitted to the court.
In summary of these circumstances, it can be seen that the lawyers involved have nothing to do with "bringing an axe to appear in court", but only for defense.
After clarifying the whole fact, the Quanzhou Municipal Law Association did not push the boat along the water, but resisted the pressure and made a decision not to punish.
This decision also stands the test of facts and laws.
As for bringing an axe as a control tool to the court without the permission of the court, it is indeed easy to cause unease and misunderstanding.
Due to security and prudence, the previous fines and judicial recommendations of the Quanzhou Middle Court are also understandable.
In order to safeguard the dignity of lawyers and prevent individual courts from making difficult laws and regulations, the Supreme People's Court issued the Rules for Judicial Police Security Inspection of People's Courts in 2014, which established the principle that lawyers do not need to conduct personal safety checks when they appear in court.
Since the release of the rule, lawyers have led by example, and there have been few incidents that endanger the security of the court due to security loopholes.
In a very few cases such as Quanzhou, as long as the spirit of mutual respect and understanding is to communicate, misunderstanding is not difficult to eliminate.
As a self-regulatory organization for the lawyer industry, the Bar Association undertakes the dual mission of punishing illegality and ensuring legal law.
In the past, individual law association organizations were criticized for their emphasis on discipline and loss of protection.
The decision of the Quanzhou Law Society, both from the process and the results, is commendable, setting an example for more law associations to perform their duties correctly.
From October 1st, which tax benefits will affect our money bags?
Xinhua News Agency, Shanghai, October 1 (Reporter Sang Tong) The new personal income tax law will come into effect on January 1, 2019, in order to allow the broad masses of the people to enjoy the tax reduction dividend as soon as possible, from October 1, will be the actual salary and salary income of taxpayers will be deducted according to the starting point of 5000 yuan per month, and the new tax rate table will be applied.
With the landing of the New Deal, what are the benefits that will affect the people's money bags?
Good one: the tax reduction of wages and salaries is obvious
Taxpayers who obtain wages and salaries after October 1 can deduct 5,000 yuan / month of basic deductions and apply the new tax rate schedule, and most taxpayers have different degrees of tax reduction, especially the tax reduction of low- and middle-income people is more obvious.
According to the tax reduction table of different income groups, after deducting the "three insurances and one gold", the monthly income of 8,000 yuan, 10,000 yuan, 20,000 yuan, 50,000 yuan, after the tax reform of the tax payable are 90 yuan, 290 yuan, 1590 yuan, 9090 yuan, compared with the starting point of 3500 yuan, the corresponding tax reduction ratio is 73.9%, 61.1%, 49.8%, 18.8%.
It is worth noting that due to the reasons of holidays, the wages that should have been paid in October by various units at the end of September in accordance with the law can apply the new basic reduction fee and tax rate table.
To this end, the withholding client software used by the tax department has provided the corresponding tax calculation function, but the corresponding tax still needs to be declared and paid during the statutory declaration period.
Benefit 2: The distance between the low tax rate and the grade is obviously enlarged
In addition to increasing the starting point, the new tax rate schedule will be applied from October 1.
The seven-trange tax rate of this wage and salary income is the same as before, and there is no change, but the tax rate distance has changed significantly, the three-grade low tax rate of 3%, 10% and 20% has been significantly expanded, and the tax rate distance of 25% has been reduced, while the three higher tax rates of 30%, 35% and 45% have remained unchanged.
It is worth noting that the tax law also adjusts the tax rate of the production and operation income, of which the lower limit of the highest-end 35% tax rate is increased from 100,000 yuan to 500,000 yuan.
This means that individual business owners and sole proprietorships will all benefit from the tax reform.
"From the early stage of the Shanghai taxpayers personal tax reduction calculation, the majority of taxpayers will fully feel the dividends of individual tax reform, especially the low- and middle-income people tax reduction is obvious."
Lan Min, head of the personal income tax department of the Shanghai Municipal Taxation Bureau of the State Administration of Taxation, said.
Benefit 3: Tax service is more convenient to optimize
Since the promulgation of the new personal income tax law, the Shanghai tax department has carried out a series of comprehensive and extensive tax publicity actions.
On the one hand, "one-to-one, peer-to-peer" policy guidance for key tax sources and key enterprises.
Pudong New Area Tax Bureau has visited Apple Trade (Shanghai) Co., Ltd., Alipay (China) Network Technology Co., Ltd., Red Star Meikailong Home Furnishing Group Co., Ltd. and other large enterprises, these enterprises have a large number of employees, withholding the payment workload is large, the tax payment amount is large, the tax department takes the initiative to guide, answer questions; Xuhui District Tax Bureau visited the region's large labor enterprises Zhongzhi Financial Consulting Co., Ltd., Zhongzhi Shanghai Economic and Technical Cooperation Company, etc.
On the other hand, for the general public taxpayers, carry out a "all-round, multi-dimensional, three-dimensional" tax policy push.
Use the official website of Shanghai Taxation, WeChat Public Number, Weibo and other channels to push policy hotspots in a timely manner to ensure that policy publicity is in place.
At the same time, since September 28th, Shanghai tax WeChat public number on-line 12366 intelligent consulting platform, through the "artificial + intelligent" tax service consultation, to carry out "targeted" intelligent integration of individual tax reform publicity services.
