Tencent said that the newly established platform and content business group (PCG, that is, Platform & Content Group), will be the original social networking business group (SNG), the original mobile Internet business group (MIG), the original network media business group (OMG) and other highly related and highly integrated sectors, with social platforms, traffic platforms, digital content, core technology and other highly integrated sectors, organic split and restructuring.
